unnormalised: **Exam Prep Apps: Chhatro-kuri koding nutun Biryani do kana?**
normalised: **Porikha Tayari App: Sikariyat Kowa Nawa Biryani Kana?**

unnormalised: Noa Exam Prep Apps do un marang competitive porikha re pass lagid lukun katha do kana? Diso-kante do nowa leka ge! IIT-JEE khon NEET, ar un baga-kan UPSC porikha khan ho, Bharat ren chhatro-kuri ko do din-din digital porao-sanghati keding jasti sapao-kanako. Un marang pustak ko do hirij tabon pe – nizor porao dandi, bohot mock test, ar okam-re ge sontoh dur class ko mone pe.
normalised: Uku porikha tayari app ko do uku soros porikha re pass lagit rahish jinish kana? Noa lekate do!

unnormalised: Testbook ar BYJU'S leka apps ko do bohot download ko nel-eda, khas-te porikha bera re. Chennai ren mit chhatro-kuri, Priya Sharma, do men-ked-a je AI-powered feedback tin-ak app use tabon unij porikha number ko do bohot jasti en-a.
normalised: IIT-JEE kho NEET porikha tak, ar uku bhoy lagao aka U P S C porikha reyo, Bharat ren sikariyat ko do besin besin Digital Parhao Sangat ko tey do bahal do.

unnormalised: Ment khan, noa do sachi-te un characha rean jogya kana? Kichu sikhak ko do screen time ar age-te tayari-len content re bharosa do chinta-eda. Noa do joto ge sori tol tapam rean katha kana, go-ko. Noa do Onam Sadhya leka mone pe – jasti payasam do okajok! Tol-tol-te do asol katha kana!
normalised: Besin besin kitabo do hirinj do, ar nijra parhao rasta, adi besin mock test ko, ar turui sandeh safa gunti ko mone do.

unnormalised: Ar nutun apps ko do 'R. D. Sharma' men-len khon ho jasti chotok te otong kan-a, noa lagid sori-te bachao do joruri kana. Apnar khoj-khobor do-pe, review ko porao-pe, ar un app do tapam pe je apnar porao rean dandi lagid sab-te sori kana. Bhaluk bhagya! Ar joto katha ko do apnar pasnao re ge tahin ma! Mon-re doho pe je break ko hatao pe, mit plate biryani rasak pe, ar apnar porikha ko do bhaluk te parom pe.
normalised: Applications like Testbook ar B Y J U ' S ko do adi besin downloads ko do nawa do, porikha samay re do adi.
Chennai ren mit sikariyat, Priya Sharma, do men ket, AI powered feedback re chalao aka mit app use lagit unij ko score do adi jold sudhar en.
Enkhan do uku do sachi re prachar katar do? Kichu sikhak ko do screen samay lagit dukhi do ar agui sajag jinish re bharosa lagit.
Sab do thik santulan koj re do, mitro.
Onam Sadhya lekate mone do – besin payasam jom lekhan do lusu do! Thik saman do ading marang jinish!
Ar nawa app ko do R. D. Sharma chetam kho adi turui dapal do, thik lekate baicha do ading joruri do.
Nijra khoj do, review ko parhao do, ar nijra parhao chalak re adi thik app do koj do.
Bujh shubhakamana, ar sab samay do ninja pakshya re do! Thahar do rahi, biryani mit plate do jom do ar porikha re top do.
